			"name": "healthCheck",
			"description": "Health check middleware with liveness and readiness probes. Kubernetes-compatible `/healthz` and `/readyz` endpoints with composable checks (database ping, memory, event loop lag, disk space) and custom check registration. Returns `200` when healthy, `503` when degraded or during shutdown drain phase, with a JSON body detailing each check.",
